Audit Trail Fields in custom table
Contents
–Add fields to the Custom DB Table
–Table Maintenance Generator
–Table Updated from the program code lines

Add fields to the Custom DB Table
• While creating the custom DB table, 
include the Audit trail structure 
ZGGL_DEV_STR_AUDIT_TRAIL

Table Maintenance Generator
• To be able to update these fields for 
the table maintenance, create the 
event


Table Maintenance Generator
• Create an event 01 and subroutine 
F_UPDATE_AUDIT_FIELDS within 
your TMG Function group


Table Maintenance Generator
• Call Include within the subroutine to 
update these fields ZGGL_DEV_REP_AUDIT_TRAIL_FIELD

Table Maintenance Generator
• Make these fields display only
• Include the program in the top main program on the function group
• Program ZGGL_DEV_DB_AUDIT_TRAIL_HIDE





